data.value: We know the Germans' sausage is famous, but we know more about Frankfurter. Bratwurst is a white sausage made from beef or pork. You can taste this sausage up to 15 cm long in the most crowded square of every city, and you can eat in the buffets selling bratwurst like toast and sausage buffets. Bratwurst of the round breads (Brötchen) among the plenty of mustard in the price is very convenient, 2-3 € is possible to eat.
